OL,6,FHundreds of people lined the streets
OL,7,Fof Hyde to say an emotional farewell
OL,8,Fto World Champion Boxer.
OL,10,FRicky Hatton's funeral cortege was led
OL,11,Fby the famous Reliant van from Only
OL,12,FFools and Horses as hundreds of people
OL,13,Flined the streets of Manchester to pay
OL,14,Ftheir respects to the "Hitman".
OL,16,FSmith concluded his eulogy by saying:
OL,17,F"Ricky was always Ricky - relatable
OL,18,Fand like by anyone and everyone - the
OL,19,Fpeople's champion.
